data.title: Sky Italia
data.meta_description: Sky Italia was formed by a merger of Tele+ and Stream TV in 2003. The logo used is the same as the one of Sky México (until 2016) and Sky Brasil. On June 28, 2010, Sky Italia and its channels adopted a new logo using the graphics of UK version of Sky (which later became its parent company in...
